This week, I made one of the biggest decisions of my life. After 25 years with the same company, I'm turning in my notice and going all-in on a dream.

Over the years, the job changed significantly, and a recent HR call confirmed that it is no longer the place for me. They announced that, despite political shifts, the company would double down and triple down on DEI rebranding it under a new name. That moment pushed me to take the leap sooner than I had planned. I stuck with them through the vaccine mandates, I refused was threatened many times to bend the knee or be fired but they finally caved, should have left then but didn't have a solid backup plan in place and that's when I started creating an escape plan.

At 60 years old, it's scary to walk away from financial security and bet it all (even the house) on something new but I've done the research, built a solid plan, and believe this is the right move. So I'm like the Invaders who arrived on shore and burned the boats, I've got to make this work. 

With the economy soon to be booming with Trumps leadership I know the business will be successful!!! Wish me luck and say a prayer us! Make small business great again!

posts.raw_content:
This week, I made one of the biggest decisions of my life. After 25 years with the same company, I'm turning in my notice and going all-in on a dream.

Over the years, the job changed significantly, and a recent HR call confirmed that it is no longer the place for me. They announced that, despite political shifts, the company would double down and triple down on DEI rebranding it under a new name. That moment pushed me to take the leap sooner than I had planned. I stuck with them through the vaccine mandates, I refused was threatened many times to bend the knee or be fired but they finally caved, should have left then but didn't have a solid backup plan in place and that's when I started creating an escape plan.

At 60 years old, it's scary to walk away from financial security and bet it all (even the house) on something new but I've done the research, built a solid plan, and believe this is the right move. So I'm like the Invaders who arrived on shore and burned the boats, I've got to make this work. 

With the economy soon to be booming with Trumps leadership I know the business will be successful!!! Wish me luck and say a prayer us! Make small business great again!
